                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_takekey_dialog1"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_takekey_dialog1",
        "message":"You get on your tiptoes and extend your hand, almost reaching it.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Just a little more...",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_takekey_dialog2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_takekey_dialog2",
        "message":"You manage to get on the very tips of your toes, very dexterous of you indeed. Almost like those fabled ballerinas from Nor City that you have only seen in books.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"[Jump and grab it.]",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_takekey_dialog3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_takekey_dialog3",
        "message":"You jump and get a hold of the key, but you fall on your behind.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Phew.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"giveItem",
                "rewardID":"dd_prison_key",
                "value":1
            },
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"dd_hidden",
                "value":23
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran_afterwin1",
        "message":"Indeed I haven't, ahem ahem.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran_afterwin2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran_afterwin2",
        "message":"Before you stands Duran Shortbeard, cousin to the Western Bogling Kings, brother to Hogrim the Mountain King, shieldbearer of the great clans, and slayer of countless maonit and assorted giantkin.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran_afterwin3"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"dd_hidden",
                "value":24
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran_afterwin3",
        "message":"Ye see, I've poured pints of ale down my throat atop piles of those reckless brutes. I know what one looks like, and I could tell ye weren't one.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"What are you doing here?",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran1"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran_introduction",
        "message":"Indeed I can, lad. It is a great honor to have the opportunity to state one's name.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran_afterwin2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran1",
        "message":"Me and the lads felt our home\u2019s gotten too tight. We set out on this expedition to find a new place to move in.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran2"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran2",
        "message":"With those creatures defeated for good, it is as good as ours. It shall be called Durandihr, \"of Duran\u2019s\" in our tongue. But you lad, deserve a reward.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"A reward's fine, but I feel like I have to clarify something to you.",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran3"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran3",
        "message":"Aye, what is it?",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"The ruins extend far beyond this room, and the monsters more vicious. Those you have seen here are on the weaker side.",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran4"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran4",
        "message":"Duran and the rest of his group get a worried expression on their faces - He looks you up and down and lowers his head in thought while stroking his beard.",
        "switchToNPC":"none",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran5"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran5",
        "message":"We'll trust you, lad. I'm a warrior myself, and I can tell you have more experience than is seen at a glance.",
        "switchToNPC":"dd_durandwarf",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran6"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran6",
        "message":"Lads, don\u2019t settle down your picks yet! We rest for a bit, then start the journey back.",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"N",
                "nextPhraseID":"dd_duran7"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran7",
        "message":"I'll give you a reward for your bravery. This is a pickaxe worthy of being held by Duran Shortbeard. Display it in your trophy room or the ale hall with pride!",
        "replies":[
            {
                "text":"Aye!",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            },
            {
                "text":"I never say no to rewards.",
                "nextPhraseID":"X"
            }
        ],
        "rewards":[
            {
                "rewardType":"questProgress",
                "rewardID":"dd_hidden",
                "value":25
            },
            {
                "rewardType":"giveItem",
                "rewardID":"dd_pickaxe",
                "value":1
            },
            {
                "rewardType":"createTimer",
                "rewardID":"dd_duran"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_duran_departure",
        "message":"We'll rest for a bit, then head back through the caverns and the passages we dug. Best of luck in whatever endeavour led you here, lad."
    },
    {
        "id":"dd_dwarfminer_departure",
        "message":"Bit sad to see this fine place go without song and fine ale ringing in its halls forevermore."
    },
